descriptions.en:
By chance, Fukaya became the lover of a very quiet and beautiful girl, Fujino, yet he worries about the vibrator she's always carrying. "Perhaps, she considers me no more fondly than that vibrator?" In fact, their relationship began when he found her using a vibrator aboard a crowded train. Although they have passionate sex, he can't be certain that she loves him, and feels threatened by her vibrator. Now, the two of them are going to a pool. As she will be unable to use the vibrator in the water, he expects they will be alone, but...

(Source: AnimeNfo)
The sixth season of Quanzhi Fashiy.

The premise of the story: "Snatch the rebel elements' secret data using the Surface! There is a leak saying that the giant coporation Ishimiya Industry will commit an act of international terrorism, and Motoko Kusanagi and the Armored Riot Police head out to seize the plug data!"

(Source: Anime News Network)

A short animation for promoting Microsoft's Surface tablet in Japan.

descriptions.en: The seventh season of Ruguo Lishi Shi Yi Qun Miao.

Deep-sea archeologist Hiroshi Ibuki is the member of the digging team working at the bottom of the sea hoping to uncover the origins of Earth's existence but instead uncovers a mysterious colony of bacteria which gives off light similar to the Aurora Borealis. The ancient bacteria, once revived, attempt to make the world habitable for themselves —a process that would bring Earth back to its early primal form, killing all current life in the process.

(Source: AnimeNFO)

titles.en: DNA² ~Dokoka de Nakushita Aitsu no Aitsu~
titles.jp: Ｄ・Ｎ・Ａ² ～何処かで失くしたあいつのアイツ～

descriptions.en:
Karin, a DNA operator from the future, is on a mission to change the course of History by stopping Junta Momonari from becoming the Mega-Playboy who fathered 100 children and led to the overpopulation of the world. But Junta is no playboy; in fact he is allergic to girls. But when Karin shoots him with the wrong DNA-altering bullet, he starts sporadically becoming the Mega-Playboy capable of charming any woman. Karin must try to restore the situation to normal before the change to Mega-Playboy becomes irreversible.

(Source: Anime News Network)

titles.jp: しおんの王 - The Flowers of Hard Blood

descriptions.en:
Shion no Ou follows the story of Yasuoka Shion, a 13-year-old Shougi player with a past of tragedy. Shion's parents were brutally murdered in front of her when she was 5 years old. The murderer sat down with her and challenged her to a game of Shougi, after telling her that if she wanted to stay alive she should forget how to speak, and forget what happened that night.

Now Shion has entered the realm of female pro Kishi, mute but strong. As her playing gathers more and more attention, so do the questions about her past and the brutal murder she witnessed. Shion's memories slowly come back, and the mystery begins to unravel, thread by thread.

titles.en: Doraemon: Nobita to Tsubasa no Yuusha-tachi
titles.jp: ドラえもん のび太と翼の勇者たち

descriptions.en:
Nobita and his friends gathered at Shizuka's house when they heard about the news about missing flocks of bird species. Nobita believed they were taken away by winged creatures and became obsessed on flying on his own. He created mechanical wings and upon the experiment he encountered an actual winged creature flying out of a time-space distortion. Upon helping him whose name is Gusuke, Nobita and his friends were sucked into the distortion and reached Gusuke's home, Birdpia or the world where the winged creatures live.

(Source: Anime News Network)

titles.jp: 劇場版　ああっ女神さまっ

descriptions.en: For centuries, a god named Celestin has been imprisoned on the moon for betraying the kingdom of Yggdrasil. Released by the fairy Morgan Le Fey, Celestin travels to Earth to reunite with his former pupil, the goddess Belldandy. Things go awry as Celestin erases Belldandy's memories of her boyfriend Keiichi and uses her as a catalyst to wreak havoc on Earth and Yggdrasil.

When a ghost girl with no legs spots a pair of disembodied tap shoes dancing to Moses Supposes from Singin' in the Rain, she joins in, gleefully providing a body to accompany their fancy footwork.

(Source: AniDB)

Long ago, in feudal Japan, there was a fierce warrior named the Demon King. He controlled a band of demons, known as the Kyouma. Only the powers of ten warriors sealed the Demon King away and kept the Kyouma under control. But now, Lord Shindigan, a powerful Kyouma is planning to free the Demon King, and the reincarnations of the ten warriors must band together and save the earth.

(Source: Anime News Network)
Original music video animated by Nebiru for the song Erase written by Deguchi Ryou and performed by Tenjin Kotone.

descriptions.en:
Ichijou Yurika is a pretty girl who is popular in her school and is also the son of the Head of Company. He enjoys a period of dating with his beloved Yuusuke whom he loves very much. But all that has changed since his father's company burned down. Then his father indirectly sold his own son to others for the sake of saving his company.

(Source: Nekopoi and Has Been Translated and Edited)
Animated short by Keiichiro Kimura about a single samurai that fights for his life against 100 of his vicious enemies.

A magician, a female doctor, a gangster, an archaeology professor, a policewoman, a drug dealer, a businessman... Such a random group of people find themselves trapped on a desolate island when they wake up from sleep one day. They are surrounded by primitive tribes, mutant viruses, and countless life and death situations on this mysterious island. What will they do to survive and escape?

titles.jp: ご愁傷さま二ノ宮くん

descriptions.it:
Shungo Ninomiya è solo una normale studentessa liceale che vive a casa con la sorella maggiore Ryoko - almeno quando è lontana dal lavoro. Tuttavia, la vita di Shungo cessa di essere una ragazza normale di nome Mayu Tsukimura che scende nel centro del campus della sua scuola in un elicottero militare. Si scopre che Ryoko ha sentito questa ragazza, insieme a suo fratello maggiore Mikihiro, a vivere nella famiglia Ninomiya.

Ma i fratelli appena arrivati ​​sono un po 'speciali: Mayu è, in effetti, una succube e suo fratello, un incubo! È una paura di uomini e donne, la paura degli uomini - e dipende dall'aiuto di tua sorella. Ryoko progetta di costringere May ad essere più vicino a Shungo, per prendere questo, usa alcuni metodi discutibili per condividere lo stesso letto e persino fare il bagno insieme.

La situazione si complica ulteriormente quando la presidentessa del consiglio studentesco Reika Houjou arriva come la nuova cameriera della famiglia Ninomiya, e non si fermerà davanti a nulla per contrastare l'allenamento sessuato di Shungo e Mayu. Con l'arrivo improvviso di tutte queste stranezze, la vita ordinaria di Shungo sta per essere gettata nel completo tumulto.

descriptions.en:
The highly anticipated HI3 anime is finally coming! 
Aren't you curious about how your favorite Valkyries fare in the kitchen, Captains? 
Join the table with Valkyries this summer for a feast of mouth-watering food and heartwarming memories.
Music video by Tarafu Ootani for the song sparkle by Japanese electronic artist Serph from his album "Aerialist."

descriptions.en: Oh Motoura and his team or rather his harem travels to a hot spring resort to train for the upcoming volleyball game. This time they got two new rookies to strengthen their effort. Little they know that they being lured in a trap set by the two beautiful newcomers.

descriptions.it: Sekai Ichi Hatsukoi racconta la storia di Onodera Ritsu, che decide di trasferirsi dalla compagnia editoriale del padre alla Marukawa Shoten, per farsi le ossa e non essere tacciato di essere un figlio di papà raccomandato ed incapace. Assegnato, suo malgrado, alla divisione Shoujo Manga, incontra l'ultima persona che avrebbe mai voluto vedere: Takano Masamune, che oltretutto è capo della sua divisione. Masamune è in realtà il senpai e primo amore dei tempi del liceo del protagonista, e il capo non ha mai dimenticato Ritsu.

descriptions.en: Short animated film by acclaimed multi-talented artist WADA Makoto. In 1964, Murder won the third ever Oofuji Noburou Award at the Mainichi Film Awards.

Murakoshi Shinta seems to be just a doctor at school. But secretly he has taken advantage of his position to hypnotize every female student he likes. Now, after putting all the targets under his control, he begins to transform the poor girl into his sex slave...

(Source: Translated from Nekopoi)

A young man discovers the true erotic touch with it he can tease almost reaching orgasm on any woman, so he decides to use it on his chosen target with some interesting results.

(Source: Anime News Network)
The story follows a young girl and her family as they get trapped in Manchuria during the Russo-Japanese War.

descriptions.it: La storia ripensa la "guerra" tra le console come un racconto fantasy: il regno di Segua vive un'antica guerra contro l'impero di Ninterudo per il dominio sulla terra di Consume. Segua è arroccata sulla difensiva, allorché si erge sulla scena un improbabile eroe nella persona di Gear, uno scavezzacollo che fa vanto della propria velocità. Gear dà una mano a sovvertire le sorti della guerra.

descriptions.en: Official music video for Kindan no Tasuketsu's song Nosferatu.

Nanase lives in a village where the stars are the most beautiful in Japan and when she hears the story of Orihime and Hikoboshi, she gazes up at the night sky every day and thinks about them. When Nanase moved to a new town, she was shocked to see the sky of the city. There are no stars in the night sky, which means that Orihime and Hikoboshi cannot meet! Nanase unconsciously writes in her notebook, "How can I make the Milky Way?"

There were three girls who happened to find her scribbling in her notebook. Riko, the leader of the group and a strong person. Mio, who loves science. Airi is a sucker for anything trendy. This is the start of a reckless attempt to create the Milky Way by the four girls, who have very different interests and personalities.

(Source: Official Announcement, Translated)

A world from which Honkai has disappeared. A journey towards the heavens. The first test flight is about to begin.

(Source: Youtube Description)

How much humiliation can four people and a penguin take?

Hard boiled Aito? Sexy bombshell Rihoko? Choji the red brief? Shining Fuusuke? Cutesy Hooter Hiroyuki? Oh, gimme a break! Who do these guys think they are? The Ninku?

Unfortunately for the real Aito, Choji, Rihoko, and Fuusuke, they do. But little did these imposters know when they stumbled on this sleepy little desert town, that there’d be a price to pay for being treated like the real Ninku, namely, having to fight the deadly Heaven & Earth brothers!

Fortunately for our phony friends, the real Aito, Choji, and Fuusuke step in, there’s nothing but trouble for the bad guys. Can the Ninku art of magic fighting beat the Heaven & Earth brothers deadly fighting style?

(Source: AniDB)
The sixth season of Ashuai.

titles.jp: たたかえ!土管くん ロボリンピック編
マシンロボ ぶっちぎりバトルハッカーズ
劇場版 少女☆歌劇 レヴュースタァライト

descriptions.en:
"Starlight" - it's a distant star, long ago, and in the far future. Two girls, who were struck by the light of the stage in this play, exchanged their destinies.

"Two people's stars, waiting on stage."

To burn out ordinary fun and joy and fulfill our destinies. A destiny to become a blast furnace at just 5 years old... what a danger. Eventually the two will meet again. One continued to stand on the stage of tragedy, the other jumped in, separated, jumped in, rewrote their destinies... and created a new chapter full of light. No girl was burned and fell from the tower, nor was she imprisoned. Then... what is the end of that new chapter?

"Starlight" is a story of an unknown author. Where does the light come from and where does it go? And who is "starring" in this story?
